## Prompt 09 — Criação da capa

```text
Create a professional and creative ebook cover for a book titled:

“AI-lucination: Between Answers and Illusions”

Author:
“Enzo C. O. Bittencourt”

Concept:
The cover should represent the idea of artificial intelligence creating answers that look real, but may be illusions.

Visual style:
- Futuristic
- Technological
- Mysterious
- Modern nonfiction ebook cover
- Dark background
- Neon blue and purple tones
- Digital fragments, circuits, holographic elements, or a humanoid AI face
